query:
WITH
              last AS (
                SELECT
                  MAX(millis) AS max
                FROM
                  occurrences
              ),
              scored AS (
                SELECT
                  skull,
                  amount,
                  COUNT(*) AS count,
                  SUM(POWER(0.5, (max - millis) / 864000000.0)) AS score
                FROM
                  occurrences
                CROSS JOIN
                  last
                GROUP BY
                  skull,
                  amount
                ORDER BY
                  score DESC
                LIMIT
                  12
              )
            SELECT
              skull AS "skull: types::SkullId",
              amount AS "amount: f32"
            FROM
              scored
